


                         ESP-r User Guide





     This directory contains the ESP-r User Guide set by section.
The following command can be used to set a section:

   tbl file | eqn | troff -ms -t | pscat | lpr -Plasername


assuming a Postscript laser writer is available. 

For those with GNU troff and groff, postscript files can be obtained
with
     gtbl file | geqn | groff -ms -t | cat > file.ps

The user guide is also in pdf format from the ESRU Web site.
Follow links to publications.
